Class Processor

  • java.lang.Object
    • todomato.Processor
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AddProcessor, DeleteProcessor, DisplayProcessor, UndoProcessor, UpdateProcessor

    public class Processor
extends java.lang.Object
    This class stores information needed to process a user's command, and contains methods to parse a command's arguments.
